Project_Title: Extracellular Vesicles (EVs) derived from Hemangioma stem cells (HemSC) (human)
Project_Description:
In order to investigate the function and mechanism of HemSC-EVs, we performed RNA-seq of HemSC-EVs which were extracted from cell culture supernatant of HemSC.
Overall design: HemSC-EVs were extracted form cell culture supernatant of HemSC by ultra-centrifuge method.  Then RNA-seq was conducted for HemSC-EVs
